<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="punish-vt">punish <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'pʌnɪʃ/    美 /'pʌnɪʃ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>惩罚；处罚：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>be heavily / severely / justly punished by law
受到法律的严重/严厉/公正惩罚</p></div>

<ul>
<li>punish sb for (doing) sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The students were punished for cheating on the exam.
这些学生因为考试作弊而受到惩罚。</p></div></div>